            <div type="translation">
                <p>Which ode is worthy of you?</p>
            </div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>Good condition. The word ποίαν is misspelled. Accents and breathings with errors. The painter probably considered the word ἐπάξιον as two words: ἐπί (preposition) and ἄξιον (epithet) adding wrong breathing in the latter. Text: Vita s. Joannis Damasceni: BHG 885c, 7:6</p>
            </div>
